						<span class="material-symbols-outlined">precision_manufacturing</span>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h4 class="font-headline-md text-on-surface mb-1">Industrial Precision</h4>
						<p class="text-on-surface-variant">We use high-grade CNC and laser machines to ensure every cut is accurate to the micron.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-start gap-gutter group">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-fixed flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg text-primary shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110">
